name: FreeSkate
description:
This is a small Skate game project I made at Plymouth University. Using the P2 physics engine.

If for some reason it doesn't load, please refresh the page. There seems to be an intermittent issue which I cannot nail down specifically!

Any Questions you may have regarding this please send them to me via Twitter: https://twitter.com/Bassforce86

The file should be visible so you're welcome to take the source and use whatever you find useful.

Thanks for looking!
